		As I mentioned, I&#8217;m trying out SpamSoap to cut down on the massive volume of spam I receive. Next week my free trial period ends, and I have to decide whether to start paying for the service at $25/month. I&#8217;m planning to pay for it. After some tweaking and whitelisting of various newsletters and mailing lists, plus a bit of configuration on my hosting account to exclude spam routed around ...
		
