<div id="post-1400" class="cf post-1400 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2006/12/check-this-prediction-in-november-2008/" title="Check this prediction in November 2008" rel="bookmark">Check this prediction in November 2008</a>
		
	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Dec</p>
			<p class="post-day">27</p>
			<p class="post-year">2006</p>				
		</div>

		I think John Edwards will be the next President of the United States. I&#8217;m not saying he&#8217;s my personal favorite of the likely candidates; he&#8217;s not, although he has many positives. I just think that, when all is said and done, he&#8217;s in the best position to win the race. A lot can happen in two years, but that&#8217;s the way it looks right now.
		
	</div>

